And I immediately started to cry and she looked at me and told me everything was ok and not to cry .I was crying so hard that I woke myself up and I was still crying . Then, as I was leaving for work the this song played, and listening to the 1st verse hit me so hard.  I love you Lena , I miss you more than ever . Until we meet again +❤+❤+❤+
justificativa: The commenter expresses love and grief, coupled with a comforting message from a deceased loved one, indicating a positive emotional response despite sadness.
